info.name: Cloudflare Radar
info.description:
The *unofficial* API documentation for Cloudflare Radar.

To start using the API, run the GET request for "Categories" under Domain Specific. This will grab an API token for use with the rest of the API, in testing they appear to expire after about an hour.
